Required modules:

pypdf (Metadata reading)
pdfrw - http://www.google.com/url?q=http://code.google.com/p/pdfrw/&sa=U&ei=cXNxT7SfK4OhiQen7dTkDw&ved=0CBEQFjAA&usg=AFQjCNGxIS2MNhkUfAMm7DGxwyrdoQNS4A (Metadata reading and writing)
wx (UI)
pybtex - BibTeX functionality
hachoir_metadata (Metadata reading)
hachoir_core (Metadata reading)
hachoir_parser (Metadata reading)
sqlalchemy (Database ORM)
gdata (Google Data)
keyring - (Encryption)
pycrypto - (Encryption)

Optional modules:

python-magic & corresponding binary library (Mimetype diagnosis)
zbar & corresponding binary library - http://pypi.python.org/pypi/zbar (Barcode scanning)
pynotify (User notifications on Linux)
